y — farmed-animal life-years caused per human DALY, times the suffering per factory-farmed life-year, times the animal&#x27;s welfare range. Under a heavy animal welfare range the penalty can exceed the human benefit, so saving human lives looks net-harmful. Only bites once animals count, so it requires animals_somewhat; and it is a near-term human-vs-animal get-off point, not combined with astronomical-stakes longtermism (no_discounting_future_humans), where x-risk dominates and the meat bookkeeping is moot. || Chain: 0 parochial → 1 far_away_humans → 2 animals_somewhat → 3 nature_intrinsic_value → 5 future_humans_matter_with_discounting → 7 animals_matter_a_lot → 8 suffering_focused → 9 meat_eater_problem" link="https://www.squiggle-language.com/playground#code=eJytWWtz27gV%2FSt3PN1WykoySVkvp%2B6MN5Y3mTrZjOM0sxNnFIiEJKxJggVIK2o2%2B9t7AJISZTNrdtQP8TAkcO655z54QX09CviCZWH6Qgb86PTo%2BJjOzs7oRjERUyrJV%2Bw%2FG1ysY7rNPMc9obVUYXAv%2BJrW7syb9WeD2Wg2nk2opVOZ0KRtAG5jAJ1rnUVJKmRM%2Fgp4p%2BRQwpT0V4KFBs6deOTSgqkZW7PNbJVFLNblA49YLCIW6pmWEV%2BvWFo%2B6VPM0kzxmYhTJWIt%2FNk9CzNePh%2FQIrPPc8BZxNKUq9lapKtZILQvszgV8bJcPtoaKhayWSi3xsaks8WCw85ytpB%2BpnlQPppQxFk6wz9sSpSchzyyjk%2BZvyK2815oYvR2k65wvRAhJ2i7e6yPKTXesSDQHVIcAREx1ySVBVO8C9FYxGFFaNxPVzzX828ajsa%2BxXhOvowSqY1f2wXYGwcciLgltEXTKYsDFsqYU4SIhz36vA3o9P6zoWq28y8J91NszIWVC4uwi33Pgv3EdUrzbEOZMWM2al517JTerZSIEvrAQ0SZ01slfwNuvvvn6Zvp9fnN9ILmG1rymCsI2Us2ZaLxQKR7Mj3Dww7FiI0lY5QEksV6H%2FtcpcblSCok11Yxna%2FN5WBJEgque%2FRuE%2FVCuYylQtxbX5NBh5LJ4FvbYtloTZwf6MWr53blnKcsv2uCzOYiFCmIzKVxOzBV8tHpkPupR5fMTyVswtccCgsSE4M47ZCWxE1iSLVE5KYf1xfnV78e%2F%2BUTzXko1ygDs9dGmH%2FBdbjBdmBDVYsF20Hmp3ksuEm9WMP9RSgz7Foh8BdFbtPZYwdRez1nbN00l%2BNvbSKbXMCED2sulitgo1IV8tlk0QpqmTzU1LqREdPi7jn9Cw6ZZ57jORBrWxlvlQD1dFNv2e25heFhb1AY5l9SxSpm2T3iZ6DhM4%2BRRlvs75vPu8AHpPPmLVcvkVgmx77nfMnBKxhY%2Bbv835lAjiNAlCCFVwUIxE5tAZwi3%2BJuxNQdT0FaaLDzeTcvi2P6cPOWFhL7kBUpQ5B9GRtP8rSwJqjlK6l11wf2He4j2RW%2F57AZEI%2FvhZJxBPMs7EbynptL0sxXYiF8DifzVvbnoe3z7ja25npYuJhgZzcVEacfyWcp06mSCXLHtLk4Y7Y3