ined with astronomical-stakes longtermism, where the cropland bookkeeping is moot. || Chain: 0 parochial → 1 far_away_humans → 2 animals_somewhat → 3 nature_intrinsic_value → 5 future_humans_matter_with_discounting → 7 animals_matter_a_lot → 8 suffering_focused → 9 meat_eater_problem → 10 net_negative_animal_lives → 18 soil_animals" link="https://www.squiggle-language.com/playground#code=eJytWWtz2zYW%2FSt3PNtdKZVkUm85651xYrnJrJNmHGcznTjDQCQkoeZrAdKymqa%2FvQcAKVG2UnNH%2B8EemgTOPffcBy%2For0cBn7M8zF4mAT86OTo%2BptPTU7qWTMSUJeRL9tsaF6uYbvKu4%2FZplcgwuBN8RSvX63o9b%2BCNvLE38VzHc8fUUFmSkjtuapybGHhnSuVRmokkJn8J2BNyKGUy8ZeChRrVnXTJpTmTHluxtbfMIxar8kGXWCwiFipPJRFfLVlWPulRzLJcck%2FEmRSxEr53x8Kcl88HNM%2FNcwvoRSzLuPRWIlt6gVB%2BkseZiBfl8tHGULGQeWGyMTYmlc%2FnHHYW3jzxc8WD8tGEIs4yDz%2FYlMpkFvJo45ZDMc%2B8mC9YJu64Z014Ia43HkI0lYiweKaMZlPmL4lthROKGL1bZ0tcz0XICdHZPlbHlGlhWBCoFkmOkIoYBhJpwCRvQ28WcRAUCvezJbeh%2BIeCRrFvMJ6Tn0RporQkmwXYGwcciLglLDWVsThgYRJzipAzYYe%2BbFJievdFU9Xb%2BX3K%2FQwbbUySuUHYZk%2FHgL3gKqNZvqZcm9EbFa86dkLvl1JEKX3kIRKE0zuZ%2FApcu%2Fun6dvp1dn19Jxma1rwmEvEoJOuy1Tlgch2ZHqGhy2KEVZDRisJJIP1Ifa5zLTLUSKRlxvFlF1r5WBpGgquOvR%2BHXXCZBEnEjFrfE0HLUong29Ng2WiNXF%2BoJevn5uVM54xe1fnB5uJUGQgMku024Gus09Oi9zPHbpgfpbAJny1UFiQ6hjEWQtpQlwnRiIXiNz00%2Br87PKX4799phkPkxUqSO81Eeb3uA7X2A5sqGqwYDvI%2FczGguusjRXcn4dJjl1LBP68KAs6fewgyrbjjI2b%2BnL8rUlkkguY8GHFxWIJbBS5RCnoLFpCLZ2HihrXScSUuH1O%2F4FD%2BlnX6ToQa1NU76QA9Wy937LbcQvDw86gMMzvM8kqZtkd4qeh4TOPkUYb7O%2Bbtw3kI9J5%2FY7LV0gsnWPfc77k0C0YGPnb%2FL%2B5QI4jQJQihZcFCMTOTAGcIN%2FidsTkLc9AWiiw83nblsUxfbx%2BR%2FME%2B5AVGUOQ%2FSTWnti0MCao4ctEqbYP7FvcR7JLfsdhMyAe3wmZxBHMs7AdJXdcX5JivhRz4XM4abvgX4e2x9ub2OrrYeFiip3tTEScfiSfZUxlMkmRO7pDxjkzvUm3JCbb1kxR7o0rFim%2BPn6PAorpD%2BeH47WkO0VvExksWa7oD7cz0Defo%2FOfQiEqO3KzqMdzISEfccTQN%2FGtZH6KlsDkGmkfo9P5AtctejG9%2BPlqaqvXINjUQLRb6AEovSjR0iASGYQMaKMAvf%2Fw5s3Z1S%2B2LtBGrRF0KohtkGY6lNTQBUNnb8%2FhoxQMQbRl1uzQNSSZ52FYlGB7tm7bK0JXQ3YYnWxTstTwDrIO2WXGJ8QuNqjoryj1XPq8bGT2faHfyDAUirgkppB7i0XIjw1DdfxPEfyrU9607dl0DbRBdB%2FdDuE4YH5