)" tooltip="&lt;b&gt;parochial + far_away_humans + animals_somewhat + nature_intrinsic_value + future_humans_matter_with_discounting + animals_matter_a_lot + suffering_focused + meat_eater_problem + soil_animals&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;Grilo&#x27;s soil-animal accounting: ~10^19 soil nematodes, mites and springtails dominate the welfare effects of almost anything. Global-health charities raise food demand and cropland (~137 m^2-yr/$ for GiveWell top charities, ~1.11 kQALY/$ of soil-animal welfare change); with soil lives net-negative, the arithmetic makes GiveWell&#x27;s top charities net-harmful. Only enters once invertebrates already count, so it requires animals_matter_a_lot; like the meat-eater problem it is a near-term get-off point, not combined with astronomical-stakes longtermism, where the cropland bookkeeping is moot. || Chain: 0 parochial → 1 far_away_humans → 2 animals_somewhat → 3 nature_intrinsic_value → 5 future_humans_matter_with_discounting → 7 animals_matter_a_lot → 8 suffering_focused → 9 meat_eater_problem → 18 soil_animals" link="https://www.squiggle-language.com/playground#code=eJytWWtz27gV%2FSt3PN1WykoySVkvp%2B6MN5Y3mTrZjOM0sxNnFIiEJKz5KkBaUbPZ394DgJQom1mzo36whyaBc88998EL%2ButRwBcsD7MXScCPTo%2BOj%2Bns7IxuJBMxZQn5kv1ng4t1TLe557gntE5kGNwLvqa1O%2FNm%2FdlgNpqNZ5OZO6aWypKU3HFbg9zGADtXKo%2FSTCQx%2BStgnpJDKZOJvxIs1JDuxCOXFkzO2JptZqs8YrEqH3jEYhGxUM1UEvH1imXlkz7FLMsln4k4kyJWwp%2FdszDn5fMBLXLz3ALOIpZlXM7WIlvNAqH8JI8zES%2FL5aOtoWIhm4XJ1tiYVL5YcNhZzhaJnyselI8mFHGWzfCDTalM5iGPtm5hXyLCWQFt9Jgyf0VsJ4pQxOjtJlvheiFCTpB991gdU6adZkGgOiQ5YiViriiRBkzyLrRkEYdxoXA%2FW3Er898U%2FI99g%2FGc%2FCRKE6Xd3S7A3jjgQMQtYampjMUBC5OYU4RkCHv0eRvr6f1nTVVv519S7mfYaPVOFgZhlxY9A%2FYTVxnN8w3l2ozeqHjVsVN6t5IiSukDDxF8Tm9l8htw7e6fp2%2Bm1%2Bc30wuab2jJYy6hby%2FdlDnIA5HtyfQMDzsUI2SGjFYSSAbrfexzmWmXo0Qi57aKKbvWysHSNBRc9ejdJuqFyTJOJGLW%2BpoOOpROBt%2FaBstEa%2BL8QC9ePTcr5zxj9q6OPZuLUGQgMk%2B024EuoI9Oh9xPPbpkfpbAJny1UFiQ6hjEWQdpQlwnRiKXiNz04%2Fri%2FOrX4798ojkPkzWqQ%2B81EeZfcB1usB3YUNVgwXaQ%2