-negative, the arithmetic makes GiveWell&#x27;s top charities net-harmful. Only enters once invertebrates already count, so it requires animals_matter_a_lot; like the meat-eater problem it is a near-term get-off point, not combined with astronomical-stakes longtermism, where the cropland bookkeeping is moot. || Chain: 0 parochial → 1 far_away_humans → 2 animals_somewhat → 3 nature_intrinsic_value → 5 future_humans_matter_with_discounting → 7 animals_matter_a_lot → 8 suffering_focused → 10 net_negative_animal_lives → 18 soil_animals" link="https://www.squiggle-language.com/playground#code=eJytWWtz2zYW%2FSt3PNtdKZVkkno7651xYrnJrJNmHGcznTijQCQkoeZrAdKymqa%2FvQcAKVG2UnNH%2B8XDiMC55577wAXz9Sjgc5aH2csk4EcnR8fHdHp6SteSiZiyhHzJflvjYRXTTe45bo9WiQyDO8FXtHKn3rQ77U%2BH09HUdabuiBoqS1JyR02NchMD7UypPEozkcTkLwF6Qg6lTCb%2BUrBQY7pjj1yaMzllK7aeLvOIxap84RGLRcRCNVVJxFdLlpVvuhSzLJd8KuJMilgJf3rHwpyX7%2Fs0z817CziNWJZxOV2JbDkNhPKTPM5EvCiXDzeGioVsGiYbYyNS%2BXzOYWcxnSd%2Brniwoe5QzLNpzBcsE3d8amGmIZ43XkAYlYiweKeMLhPmL4ltxRGKGL1bZ0s8z0XICfpvX6tjyrTzLAhUiyRH0EQMA4k0YJK3oSmLOJgLhd%2BzJbdy%2F0NBh9g3GM%2FJT6I0UdrtzQLsjQMORPwkLDWVsThgYRJzipAVYYe%2BbII%2Bufuiqert%2FD7lfoaNVvdkbhC2%2BdExYC%2B4ymiWrynXZvRGxauOndD7pRRRSh95iCTg9E4mvwLX7v5p8nZydXY9OafZmhY85pJlvJOuy2Tkgch2ZHqGly2KETpDRisJJIP1Ifa5zLTLUSKRexvFlF1r5WBpGgquOvR%2BHXXCZBEnEjFrfE37LUrH%2FW9Ng2WiNXZ%2BoJevn5uVM54x%2B2sqkxmbiVBkIDJLtNuBrqRPTovczx26YH6WwCZ8tVBYkOoYxFkLaUJcJ0YiF4jc5NPq%2FOzyl%2BO%2FfaYZD5MVqkTvNRHm93gO19gObKhqsGA7yP3MxgLR48h8uD8Pkxy7lgj8eZH6dPrYQZRmxxkZN%2FXj6FuTyCQXMOHDiovFEtgoZMmZKZ4l1NJ5qKhxnURMidvn9B84pN95judArE3hvJMC1LP1fstuxy0MDzr9wjC%2FzySrmGV3iJ%2BGhs88RhptsL9v3jaJj0jn9TsuXyGxdI59z%2FmSg1cwMPK3%2BX9zgRxHgChFCi8LEIidmQI4Qb7F7YjJW56BtFBg5%2FO2LYtj%2Bnj9juYJ9iErMoYg%2B0msPbFpYUxQw5eJUm0f2Lf4Hcku%2BR2HzYB4fCdkEkcwz8J2lNxx%2FUiK%2BVLMhc%2FhpO10fx3aLm9vYqufB4WLKXa2MxFx%2BpF8ljGVySRF7uguGOfM9CbdkphsWzNFuTeuWKT4%2Bvg9CiimP5wfjteS7hS9TWSwZLmiP9xOX%2F%2F4HN39FApR2XWbRT2eCwn5iCOGvolvJfNTtAQm10j7GJ3OF3hu0YvJxc9XE1u9BsGmBqLdQg9A6UWJlgaRyCB