negative — every human sustained means more net-negative farmed lives. Presupposes counting wild/invertebrate animals, so it requires animals_matter_a_lot; and like the meat-eater problem it is a near-term animal get-off point, not combined with astronomical-stakes longtermism (no_discounting_future_humans). || Chain: 0 parochial → 1 far_away_humans → 2 animals_somewhat → 3 nature_intrinsic_value → 5 future_humans_matter_with_discounting → 7 animals_matter_a_lot → 9 meat_eater_problem → 10 net_negative_animal_lives" link="https://www.squiggle-language.com/playground#code=eJylWG1v2zgS%2FiuD4PbOztmOJL%2B7lwPSxtkWl3aLJEWxqAuVlmibF4nSkZQdXzf7229ISrYc6xAB%2FpBEkchnnnnlDH%2BehXRBski9S0J6Njm7uIDLy0t4EIRxUAkEgvx3iw8bDrPMc9webBIRhWtGN7Bxfc%2Fv%2Bn1%2F6I9914GGVEkKrtPUEDOOUFdSZnGqWMIhWCHiBBxIiUiCFSORBnTHHriwIMInG7L1V1lMuCw%2BeEA4i0kkfZnEdLMiqvjSBU5UJqjPuBKMSxb4axJltPjeh0VmvltAPyZKUeFvmFr5IZNBknHF%2BLJYPtwJyhcSP0p2wsYQU6J8%2FMEvqUjmEY133B3gVPmcLolia%2BpbHD%2FCZ2ksMCXBCsjeDEwCgc9btcLnBYsooJn3n%2BUFKK0mCUPZAkHRN4xTCYkwYIK20XokpsiESXyvVtQa9m8SNeaBwXgDQRKnidQK7hbgXh5SRMRXzFKTivCQRAmnEKPzow782Pl2uv6hqert9CmlgcKN1sLJwiDsw6BjwN5SqWCebSHTYvRGScuKTeB%2BJVicwlcaobspfBbJvxHX7v51%2Bml6d%2FUwvYb5FpaUU4HG7qTbIuZoyNSBmc7xYws4OsmQ0ZZEJIP1hQdUKK1ynAiMsp3FpF1rzUHSNGJUduB%2BG3eiZMkTgY5r%2FEz7LUjH%2FeemwTLeGju%2FwLsPb8zKOVXEvtWBQOYsYgqJzBOtdqgT5pvTAvd7B25IoBKUibpaKFyQah9w1QKZANWBkYglem76bXN9dfv7xV%2B%2Bw5xGyQbzQe81HqZP%2BBxtcTtio1UNFsoOs0BZX1Adnlyi%2BjYnvqJPt5%2BpeI%2FW1Ya%2BPFYR07DjuEbRCXjPTQAENRza9D8ZQ0cjS0jRj6scBCUqEwUTNDpvx0Q8UoXkmFQU7d22sXEBXx8%2BwyLBfWgaRVDTIOFrdIe1jREBjUAkUrYDxH7E9%2BhxQdcUZYZA%2BZqJhMconkTtOFlT%2FQiSBIItWEDRKzaxr%2FMkrtauS9vOKFdPPw9yFVPc2VYspvB3CIgiUokkRQPqpOcZMQmq85KIthWTx3zjjsSSbi%2FuMYo4%2FOn8crEVsJbwKRHhimQS%2FnQ7ff3yDRazS7QQFEWmmQflNRNoPqCLhf6DMkruTzEviNii7zmme8DwuQVvpze%2F3U1tCBuEDWXLlS5aLUwEjL840aZBTyg0ZAg7C8D9l48fr%2B5%2Bt8GBtcQKwXRFYxukuXYlNHTUwNWna9RRMIJOtLHW7MADmmSRRVEeh%2B35tm2fAFMbo8PYyWampYZl1Spklxmd0HfcoGKRwXjPRECLbDbVURc%2BHbwR4wUxibG3XEb0wjCUF%2F9g4T87xUtb