 makes GiveWell&#x27;s top charities net-harmful. Only enters once invertebrates already count, so it requires animals_matter_a_lot; like the meat-eater problem it is a near-term get-off point, not combined with astronomical-stakes longtermism, where the cropland bookkeeping is moot. || Chain: 0 parochial → 1 far_away_humans → 2 animals_somewhat → 3 nature_intrinsic_value → 5 future_humans_matter_with_discounting → 7 animals_matter_a_lot → 10 net_negative_animal_lives → 18 soil_animals" link="https://www.squiggle-language.com/playground#code=eJylWG1v2zgS%2FiuD4PbOztmOJL%2B7lwPSxtkWl3aLJEWxqAuXlmibF4nSkZQVXzf7229ISrYc6xAB%2FtIqFvnMM%2B8z%2BnkW0CVJQ%2FUuDujZ5OziAi4vL%2BFBEMZBxeAL8t8tPmQcZqnnuD3IYhEGG0YzyNy5N%2B%2FO%2B%2FPh3HXm7ggaUsUJuKOmxphxxLqSMo0SxWIO%2FhohJ%2BBAQkTsrxkJNaI79sCFJRFzkpHtfJ1GhMvihQeEs4iEci7jiGZrooo3XeBEpYLOGVeCccn8%2BYaEKS3e92GZmvcWcB4RpaiYZ0yt5wGTfpxyxfiqOD7cCcoPknkY74S5DnCq5pyuiGIbOrdn5yE%2B76ii9jJmYf5OGuWnxF8D2VuASSDweavW%2BLxkIQU08f61vAClNSRBIFsgKPqFcRQQCwMmaBsNRyKK9JjE39WaWpv%2BTaKy3DcYb8CPoySWWrfdAbzLA4qI%2BBOz1KQiPCBhzClE6PiwAz92fp1ufmiq%2Bjp9Sqiv8KI1brw0CPsQ6Biwt1QqWKRbSLUYfVHSsmITuF8LFiXwlYboaQqfRfxvxLW3f51%2Bmt5dPUyvYbGFFeVUEEU7ybaINxowdWCmc3zZAo7%2BMWS0JRHJYH3hPhVKqxzFAgNsZzFpz1pzkCQJGZUduN9GnTBe8Vigzxo%2Fk34LknH%2FuWmwjLfGzi%2Fw7sMbc3JBFbG%2FJiJekAULmUIii1irHehk%2Bea0wP3egRviqxhloq4WCg8k2gdctTBMgOrAiMUKPTf9ll1f3f5%2B8ZfvsKBhnGEq6LvGw%2FQJn8MtXkdstKrBQtlB6ivrC%2FQexfBG9W06fEWfbj9T8R6tqw19eawiZmDHcY2iE%2FCemwAIaji06X9Sho5GlpCgH9c5CEpUJgomaHTejoh4pArJMako2rttY%2BMCvj58hmWM99A0iqCmfsw36A5rGyMCGr6IpWz7iP2Iv6PHBd1QlBkA5RsmYh6heBK2o3hD9SNI4gu2ZD5Fr9icvs7zt1q7Lm07o1w9%2FTzIVUzwZluxiMLfwSeKSCXiBA2o852nxCSozksi2lZMHvONOxJJur24xyji8Kfzy8VWwEbCp1gEa5JK%2BNPt9PWPb7COXaKFoKgvzTwor5lA8wFdLvV%2FKKPk%2FgTzgogt%2Bp5juvsMn1vwdnrz293UhrBByChbrXW9amEiYPxFsTYNekKhIQPYWQDuv3z8eHX3uw0OrCVWCKYrGtsgLbQroaGjBq4%2BXaOOghF0oo21Zgce0CTLNAzzOGwvtm37BJjaGB3GTjYzLTWsqFYhe8zohL7jBhWLDMZ7KnxaZLMtmrq3oKCQ8YKYxNhbrUJ6YRjKi3%2Bw4J%2Bd4kdbo0zqYC3AFNQ1ARVHmN8%2BTSEJiZWVF0piAgvj