 height="140" as="geometry"/></mxCell></object><object label="Suffering-focused&lt;br&gt;ethics&lt;br&gt;[1+2+3+5+8]&lt;br&gt;→ The Humane League&lt;br&gt;   73 lives-eq/$1k · 98% best&lt;br&gt;   runner-up Rainforest Trust · 2%&lt;br&gt;(Brian Tomasik, David Pearce)" tooltip="&lt;b&gt;parochial + far_away_humans + animals_somewhat + nature_intrinsic_value + future_humans_matter_with_discounting + suffering_focused&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;Asymmetry: averting intense suffering takes priority over creating happiness. Factory farming, malaria and the worst wild-animal conditions weigh up; speculative future-flourishing bets weigh down. Arises most naturally from taking animal suffering seriously, so it requires animals_somewhat. || Chain: 0 parochial → 1 far_away_humans → 2 animals_somewhat → 3 nature_intrinsic_value → 5 future_humans_matter_with_discounting → 8 suffering_focused" link="https://www.squiggle-language.com/playground#code=eJylWP1z27gR%2FVd2PL1WykkySVlfTt0ZJ5YvmTq5jO00cxNnFIiEJNT8KkBaUXO5v%2F0eAFKiLLlhql88tAi8fbv7sNjl16OAz1geZi%2BTgB%2BdHh0f09nZGd1KJmLKEvIl%2B%2B8KD8uY7nLPcU9omcgweBB8SUt34k26k95kSA2VJSkNm3rzXQyQc6XyKM1EEpO%2FANYpOZQymfgLwUIN5Y48cmnG5IQt2WqyyCMWq%2FKFRywWEQvVRCURXy5YVr7pUsyyXPKJiDMpYiX8yQMLc16%2B79EsN%2B8t4CRiWcblZCmyxSQQyk%2FyOBPxvFw%2BJJXPZhxI88ks8XPFA0N%2FzPwFsY0PQhGjd6tsgeeZCDkhOpvX6pgyzZEFgWqR5AipiLmiRBowydtwnUUcTITC79mC26j8TYFu7BuM5%2BQnUZoozW69AHvjgAMRPwll0FTG4oCFScwpQs7CDn1ep2T88FlT1dv5l5T7GTba8CQzg7DJXseAveAqo2m%2Bolyb0RsVrzp2SrfAeqVjyemKs3nO7cZfxm%2FH1%2Be34wuarmjOYy5ZxjvpqlQJD0S2FaFneNmiOMksDx1EIBms97HPZaa9jRIJdayDpexaGwmWpqHgqkM3q6gTJvM4kVBI42vaa1E66n1rGiyTqJHzE718%2FdysnPKM2V9TmUzZVIQiA5Fpoj0OtMQ%2FOi1yP3XokvlZAptMcguFBakOf5y1SCXEtSYSOUfSxh%2BXF%2BdXvx3%2F5RNNeZgsoWO91ySXf8FzuMJ2YCOgBgu2g9zPbBqQOA5twv1ZmOTYtUDOLwpx0tmugzg8HWdo3NSPw29NIqMrYMKHJRfzBbBx1CRnRt4LREtLUFHjNomYEvfP6V9wSL%2FzHM9BsNbCfycFqGer%2FZbdjlsY7nd6hWH%2BJZOsYpY9IH8aGj7zGApaYz9t3h7jD1Dy6h2Xr6BVxP1J50sOXsHAhL%2FN%2F5MLyBsJohTqXRQgCHZmtH8KvcXtiMl7noG0UGDn87Y9Ec